        <abstract> 
<p>Glad to hear about colours of <hi rend="italic">Hylobates</hi>.</p>  
<p>Cannot find any statement about which digits in man are most subject to syndactylism in Isidore Geoffroy [Saint-Hilaire]’s <hi rend="italic">Histoire des anomalies</hi> [1832–7].</p> 
            <p>Asks questions concerned with seasonal and sexual changes in plumage of various bird species.</p>
            <p>Does male woodpecker share in incubation?</p>
        </abstract>
